{
  "stem": "13213.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there they had more Jewish families.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had a cheder there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father used to teach us in our own house with some other neighbors' kids.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's hard to say.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother seemed to be very good natured-- my father too, getting along very well with the neighbors.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from what I saw, the way the neighbors took care of us and helped us during the war to feed us, and helped us to-- to hide us from the Germans and the Nazis, I find it was really a legacy, which was left that the people really cared for us and because we cared for our neighbors.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's hard to say.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because their life was a very hard life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You worked day and night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother, with six kids, had to do all the housework, and wash the laundry in the river, and get the water from the well across in the village.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- but we had a lot of entertainment with some of the Jewish neighbors, with the neighbors from the villages, my grandparents that lived in the next village, called [?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Korist. ?] And also, a lot of the neighbors used to come in and gather in our house.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember staying up till late at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were always talking, and discussing politics, and everything else, like today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the village itself, I would say, was maybe about 120, 130 families.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then surrounding, there were big farmers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were, around there, about maybe another 30, 40 home-- families in there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were only-- in our village, there was my aunt and uncle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother's sister got married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her name was Beila.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
